data.name: lb_instructions.Text
data.value: Click Dispense to simulate the action of refuelling a vehicle. To stop refuelling, click Stop. You will see plenty of stats on the left, which will help you see what is going on. Once you simulated, click “add to totals” to save current stats. To reset the simulator, click Reset. You'll be notified when there is no more fuel to dispense. When notified, you'll need to add a final transaction to the totals and click Reset. For help, click Help.
